{"about_the_game":"<p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1155330/extras/Discord_image.png?t=1729068175\" /></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\"><strong>In a dystopian future where corporations rule, a brutal reality show is the hottest entertainment property in town! You play as Scarlett Martillo, a contestant out for revenge. To win, you must navigate dangerous urban arenas packed with lethal traps and face off against hordes of heavily-armed psychopaths.</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1155330/extras/1_ShowGunners_Gameplay_600x250.gif?t=1729068175\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1155330/extras/Pure_Turn-Based_Tactical_Combat_600x39.png?t=1729068175\" />Each stage in Showgunners has been hand-crafted to create a curated, turn-based tactical gameplay experience, heightened with the inclusion of a diabolical show director that can hinder Scarlett or help her opponents depending on your performance. This dynamic level design ensures that no two levels play the same way and keep players thinking tactically. Showgunners has been built to challenge and delight players, whether they\u2019re a turn-based tactical game initiate or a long-time fan of the genre!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1155330/extras/2_ShowGunners_Breaching_600x219.gif?t=1729068175\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1155330/extras/Fight_Alongside_Unique_Characters_600x39.png?t=1729068175\" />Scarlett won\u2019t be fighting alone. As the story progresses, players will recruit new partners that can turn the tide of battle in all kinds of exciting ways. Upgrade your characters by spending talent points in their unique skill trees and outfitting them with weapons bought at a shop or earned during battle. Hidden challenges within each chapter can unlock more allies, legendary weapons, and helpful items, so be sure to keep an eye out!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1155330/extras/3_ShowGunners_Ronin_600x219.gif?t=1729068175\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1155330/extras/Face_the_Competition_600x39.png?t=1729068175\" />Players will need to navigate an obstacle course of deadly traps and lethal puzzles in real-time, but be prepared for an ambush at any corner. Psychopathic enemies like the Ogre and the Ronin aren\u2019t the only deadly elements you\u2019ll need to overcome. Combat scenarios are peppered with unique environmental hazards, from ticking time bombs to runaway trains. There is never a dull moment in Showgunners!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1155330/extras/4_ShowGunners_Shooting_600x219.gif?t=1729068175\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1155330/extras/Become_a_Star_of_the_Show_600x39.png?t=1729068175\" />Gain fame by avoiding death, surviving rounds, and eliminating your enemies with gruesome panache. The more you succeed, the more fans you earn; your growing fame will yield increasingly beneficial sponsorship deals.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1155330/extras/4.gif?t=1729068175\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1155330/extras/Take_the_combat_to_Twitch!_600x39.png?t=1729068175\" />Streamers, rejoice! Use the native Twitch integration to keep audiences engaged by letting them control the direction of each level. They can add more enemies, change the terrain, add or remove obstacles, or send useful items, all from chat.</p>","achievements":{"highlighted":[{"name":"Star","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/1155330/c5ce89ac5330a18553e2e27a67de3055a62e4d35.jpg"},{"name":"Superstar","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/1155330/12d7e2698912c0cd40321a98ad04ac64c27f0729.jpg"},{"name":"Legend","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/1155330/2c0d9afdcbcdcb4663f4c76090d672db659d06b7.jpg"},{"name":"Season Premiere","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/1155330/2df8f268e9e812315dafb994bb760f9615c842df.jpg"},{"name":"Old Quarter","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/1155330/6363d267b4781e40ed8b53454872701713a68516.jpg"},{"name":"Abandoned Housing Block","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/1155330/9cded0645dd8f49251aa1c3fcc937b0a5c3a173c.jpg"},{"name":"Metro Central","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/1155330/380e61c7da33ea8205cd1bd5221491aefb018f69.jpg"},{"name":"Industrial Zone","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/1155330/14cd6b3397bef91bda707fc2b3b7a294240c4ba8.jpg"},{"name":"Disaster Area","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/1155330/0c011af2112071aa5c665e6ef8a7840f51708356.jpg"},{"name":"Amber Harbor","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/1155330/4cf4a7d33